<p><q>The <qex>d⟦ae⟧dal</qex> hand of Nature.</q> <rj><qau>J.
Philips.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The doth the <qex>d⟦ae⟧dal</qex> earth throw forth to thee,⟦br⟧
